model

Class CountryDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.CountryDetails

  • public class CountryDetails
extends java.lang.Object
    CountryDetails class have all the details of countries related to the selected .map file. It also maintains a list of it's neighboring Countries.

      • CountryDetails

        public CountryDetails(java.lang.String p_index,
                      java.lang.String p_countryId,
                      java.lang.String p_continentIndex,
                      java.lang.String p_xCoOrdinate,
                      java.lang.String p_yCoOrdinate,
                      GameMap p_map)
        Creates CountryDetails object as per the argument parameters. This constructor used while reading from ".map" files.
        Parameters:
        p_index - index in the ".map" file as per Domination's conventions
        p_countryId - ID of the country
        p_continentIndex - index of the continent this country belongs to
        p_xCoOrdinate - x-coordinate on GUI map
        p_yCoOrdinate - y-coordinate on GUI map
        p_map - GameMap in which this country resides
